<scopecontent>
<head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>This collection contains three diaries of T.M.N. Jones, describing his service in the Cavalry of the Confederate Army from September 24, 1863 to May 23, 1865. There is a typed transcript of the same. The collection is in two file folders.</p>
</scopecontent>
